OL,3,CJSO ruling sets precedent for harsher
OL,4,Csentencing of protesters, barrister
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSixteen activists were sentenced last
OL,8,Fyear for their roles in four
OL,9,Fdemonstrations held by JSO between
OL,10,FAugust and November 2022, leading to a
OL,11,Fgroup challenge at the Court of Appeal
OL,12,Fwhich concluded on Friday.
OL,14,FHallam was jailed for five years for
OL,15,Fagreeing to disrupt traffic by having
OL,16,Fprotesters climb onto gantries over
OL,17,Fthe M25 for four successive days, with
OL,18,Fother protesters sentenced for
OL,19,Fclimbing on gantries over the motorway
OL,20,Fand throwing soup over Vincent van
OL,21,FGogh's Sunflowers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
