OL,3,CJSO ruling sets precedent for harsher
OL,4,Csentencing of protesters, barrister
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"The importance of the process is that
OL,8,Fthe courts are now recognising that
OL,9,Fhigher sentences and more severe
OL,10,Fsentences normally reserved for
OL,11,Fprotest with violence can now be
OL,12,Fhanded out for protest and other
OL,13,Faggravating features, such as a high-
OL,14,Flevel disruption or individuals that
OL,15,Fare at the higher echelons of the
OL,16,Forganisation or the complexity of the
OL,17,Foperation," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
