OL,3,CJSO ruling sets precedent for harsher
OL,4,Csentencing of protesters, barrister
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"So there's a whole panoply of
OL,8,Fsentencing opportunities for the
OL,9,Fcourts now which still exist from
OL,10,Fcommunity service to fines and in
OL,11,Fthese circumstances to prison
OL,12,Fsentences.
OL,14,F"The key significance of today is very
OL,15,Fstraightforward - it's that the level
OL,16,Fof sentences have now increased.
