OL,3,CJSO ruling sets precedent for harsher
OL,4,Csentencing of protesters, barrister
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"I do emphasise these are unusual, and
OL,8,FI don't think it's sending out a
OL,9,Fsignal that necessarily the normal
OL,10,Frank and file sentences for public
OL,11,Fprotest are going to change."
OL,13,FCooper said the significance of
OL,14,FFriday's ruling is that it sends "a
OL,15,Fdeterrent message as far as the courts
OL,16,Fare concerned that those who engage in
OL,17,Forganised, repetitive, and disruptive
OL,18,Fprotesting are liable to pretty long
OL,19,Fperiods of imprisonment".
