OL,3,CJSO ruling sets precedent for harsher
OL,4,Csentencing of protesters, barrister
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe said there are now "very few
OL,8,Foptions as far as the appeal process
OL,9,Fis concerned", and that while there
OL,10,F"may well be challenges" regarding
OL,11,Fhuman rights or freedom of speech, he
OL,12,Fthought these legal bids "won't
OL,13,Fimpinge upon the sentencing process".
OL,15,FIn a statement, Just Stop Oil
OL,16,Fdescribed the ruling as a "another
OL,17,Fnail in the crucifixion of justice".
